snippet.title: Reincarnated - Full No Commentary Playthrough
snippet.description:
Reincarnated is a fanmade game based on Garten of Banban, the Indie Mascot Horror game based on the likes of Bendy and the Ink Machine, Poppy Playtime, Choo Choo Charles, and Five Nights at Freddy's has taken then internet by storm. In today's video we attempt to recreate the game in ONLY A WEEK with ZERO game development experience. We're calling it Reincarnated.

IN THE EVENT THAT THE EUPHORIC BROTHERS WOULD LIKE THE GAME OR THESE VIDEOS TAKEN DOWN, I WILL DO SO IMMEDIATELY. JUST SHOOT ME A DM ON TWITTER ON EMSSAGE ME AT MY BUSINESS EMAIL. THE LAST THING I WANT TO DO IS INFRINGE ON THEIR WORK, THIS WAS JUST A PRACTICE PROJECT FOR FUN FOR ME TO LEARN GAME DESIGN. 

This is a fanmade project and video based on "Garten of Banban" by the Euphoric Brothers. This project was made purely for practice and fun and is not for profit. Please support the official releases of the Garten of Banban series. 

Download the game here: https://uniquegeese.itch.io/garten-of-banban-reincarnated

SEE HOW IT WAS MADE: https://youtu.be/34HLlRRd2XQ

Thanks to Slushy, Pincer, and Seek for help on development. (I'll update this with their links soon).

WATCH ME LIVE ► https://www.twitch.tv/uniquegeese
Join the Discord ►  https://discord.gg/4aQfD2JM6Q
Follow my Twitter ► https://twitter.com/UniqueGeese?lang=en
Merch ► https://uniquegeese.creator-spring.com/

Wanna send me some mail? It WILL be opened on stream and maybe even a video!
Mason M. 
PO Box 583
Mattoon, IL 61938

Outro music by DPZ for the VS UniqueGeese - Feathery Fight Soundtrack: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V5FwpOwJR8Y
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=brycHy-eGyk

My Singing Monsters is a 2012 video game & virtual band franchise developed by Big Blue Bubble and published by Canada Media Fund. The first game of the series was released on September 4, 2012, for Apple iOS. Breed and feed hundreds of quirky musical Monsters to form your own orchestra in this award-winning game! With so many catchy tunes and hundreds of Monsters to collect, you’ll be addicted to this monstrously fun game before you know it.

Friday Night Funkin' is an open-source donationware rhythm game first released in 2020 for a game jam. The game was developed by a team of four Newgrounds users, Cameron "Ninjamuffin99" Taylor, David "PhantomArcade" Brown, Isaac "Kawai Sprite" Garcia, and evilsk8r.

THESE FNF MODS ARE SO GOOD?! Like Garcello, Sonic.EXE, StickyBM, Ruv, MidFight Masses, Hypno's Lullaby, Monochrome, Indie Cross, Undertale, Cuphead, Bendy, sans, Hotline 025, Pac Man, Hecker, Entity, Twinsomnia, DDLC, Monika, Freddy, Ourple Guy, FNAF at Freddy's, Markiplier, Geese, Zardy, Zardy B-Sides, Baldi's Basics, and more FNF Mods like that that are popular. I love playing all these mods and more like Imposter Among Us, D-Sides, Bat Man, Pibby, Neo, Fall Guys, MultiVersus, and other crazy worlds. 

#GartenofBanban2 #GartenofBanban #UniqueGeese
